id;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:12px;margin-bottom:16px;\">\n    <div style=\"background:white;border-radius:12px;padding:16px;text-align:center;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#6B7280;margin-bottom:4px;\">대출 한도</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#DC2626;\">최대 600만원</div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"background:white;border-radius:12px;padding:16px;text-align:center;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#6B7280;margin-bottom:4px;\">대출 기간</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#DC2626;\">만기 1년</div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"background:white;border-radius:12px;padding:16px;text-align:center;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#6B7280;margin-bottom:4px;\">금리</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#DC2626;\">저금리</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  \n  <div style=\"background:white;border-radius:8px;padding:12px;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:14px;color:#7F1D1D;line-height:1.6;\">✓ 은행권 저금리 대출로 폐업 후 점포 철거비용 부담 완화<br>✓ '2026년 경제성장전략'에 따른 신규 정책</div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<h3>새출발기금 재기지원사업 대폭 확대</h3>\n\n<div style=\"margin:24px 0;\">\n  <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:24px;margin-bottom:24px;\">\n    <div style=\"text-align:center;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#6B7280;margin-bottom:4px;\">2025년</div>\n      <div style=\"background:#E5E7EB;border-radius:50%;width:80px;height:80px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-weight:700;color:#6B7280;font-size:14px;\">부산만</div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:32px;color:#10B981;\">→</div>\n    <div style=\"text-align:center;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#10B981;margin-bottom:4px;\">2026년</div>\n      <div style=\"background:#10B981;border-radius:50%;width:100px;height:100px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-weight:700;color:white;font-size:16px;\">전국 9개</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  \n  <div sty